channel.title: New York Society of Pediatric Critical Care Medicine
channel.description: Welcome to the webiste of the New York Society of Pediatric Critical Care Medicine. Our mission is to provide a venue for people interested in Pediatric Critical Care in the TriState area. We provide opportunities for education and networking.

item.title: Welcome to New York Society of Pediatric Critical Care Medicine Website!
item.description: Welcome to the New York Society of Pediatric Critical Care Medicine website. We will be updating this website periodically with events and information relevant to the society as well as to Pediatric Critical Care Medicine in the TriState area.
